'''''A United Kingdom''''' ni romantic drama film yasohotse muri 2016 muri [[Botswana]] iyoborwa na Amma Asante yanditswe na Guy Hibbert<ref>A United Kingdom (2016) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>, ishingiye ku urugo nyakuri, ubuzima hagati ya Seretse Khama<ref>A United Kingdom movie review (2017) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › a-united-kingd...</ref>, kuragwa ubutegetsi kwa Bechuanaland ( yari perezida wa [[Botswana]])<ref>A United Kingdom - BBC Film <nowiki>https://www.bbc.co.uk</nowiki> › bbcfilm › films › a-united-kin...</ref>,  n'umugore we Ruth Williams Khama .  David Oyelowo na Rosamund Pike bagaragaza Seretse na Ruth<ref>A United Kingdom review – black king to white queen… | A United Kingdom | The Guardian</ref>.

Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto mu 2016<ref>'A United Kingdom': A true love story gets mired in global politics <nowiki>https://www.washingtonpost.com</nowiki> › movies › 2017/02/16</ref>,  kandi ni yo filime yatangiye iserukiramuco rya sinema rya 60 rya London<ref>A United Kingdom - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › a_united_kingdom</ref>. 

