== uko yakozwe ==
Pike yinjiye mu bakinnyi muri Gicurasi 2015, Asante yinjira nyuma gato<ref>A United Kingdom movie review (2017) | Roger Ebert</ref>.  Muri Nzeri 2015, Asante yatangaje ko gufata amashusho bizagabanywa hagati ya [[Botswana]] na London<ref>A United Kingdom Review | Movie - Empire <nowiki>https://www.empireonline.com</nowiki> › movies › reviews › un...</ref>, kandi ko bizatangira mu Kwakira mu rwego rwo kwitegura irekurwa rya filimi muri 2016 rihurirana n’imyaka 50 y'ubwigenge muri [[Botswana]]<ref>A United Kingdom vs True Story of Seretse Khama and Ruth Williams (historyvshollywood.com)</ref>.  Mu Kwakira 2015, Jack Davenport na Tom Felton bifatanije n'aba bakinnyi<ref>A United Kingdom · BIFA · British Independent Film Awards</ref>.  Mu Gushyingo 2015, amashusho amwe yabereye hafi ya Hyde Park / Kensington Gardens harimo na Imperial College Union<ref>A United Kingdom - Full Cast & Crew - TV Guide <nowiki>https://www.tvguide.com</nowiki> › movies › cast</ref> . Umukinnyi wa sinema yari Sam McCurdy naho umuyobozi wa filimi  yari Simon Bowles<ref>A United Kingdom - Simon Bowles <nowiki>http://www.simonbowles.com</nowiki> › auk</ref> 

